description.narrative: The proposed Project will support the Department of Antioquia's long-term vision to improve the employability of young people a nd increase the competitiveness of the labor force by: (i) increasing equitable access and retention in upper-secondary education, (ii) improving equitable educational achievement in upper-secondary education, and (iii) increasing the proportion of public school secondary-education graduates who continue on to tertiary education.
